1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to postsecondary education; to require each
2 public or private two-year or four-year college or university
3 provide a report to the Attorney General and the Legislature
4 relating to certain funding from a foreign source as prescribed; to
5 provide powers and duties to the Attorney General; and to provide a
6 civil penalty.
7 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
